      "description": "Presenting a rare, collector-grade example that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a complete, chronological binder of every service performed at the authorized dealership. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, this vehicle is for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. It is, quite simply, as close to a new car as a pre-owned vehicle can get.",
